-- Temasek Raises Stake in Copper Producer Turquoise Hill to 3.7%
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   D o n v i l l e
-- 2012-11-14T14:22:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-14/temasek-raises-stake-in-copper-producer-turquoise-hill-to-3-7-.html
Temasek Holdings Pte,  Singapore ’s
state-owned investment company, raised its stake in Rio Tinto
Group’s  Turquoise Hill Resources Ltd. (TRQ)  unit to 3.7 percent in the
third quarter, according to a filing.  Temasek holds 36.6 million shares of Vancouver-based
Turquoise Hill, an increase of 31.4 million shares from the
preceding quarter, according to a filing today with the U.S.
Securities and Exchange Commission. The stake has a market value
of $297 million.  To contact the reporter on this story:
